public abstract class JetmBeanDefinitionParser
extends org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.AbstractBeanDefinitionParser

Base class for our Spring BeanDefinitionParsers. This class alters the behavior of AbstractBeanDefinitionParser such that it automatically assign a id if none is given.
